## LocKeyChange

LocKeyChange is a simple program that allows you to change other user's windows password. You can view it here.

## LocKrypthography

LocKrypthography is a windows program that allows you to encrypt and decrypt files with a password. I am currently working on it so it isn't very complete. Anyway, you can view it here.

## Social Networks

You can follow me on Gbatemp and on Youtube. You can also contact me on lockcracking@gmail.com.
